1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
Sub by Dramacool.ae

2
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

3
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

4
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

5
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

6
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

7
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

8
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

9
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

10
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

11
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

12
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

13
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

14
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

15
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

16
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
<i>Legend of Fei</i>

17
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
<i>Episode 34</i>

18
00:01:38,140 --> 00:01:40,580
<i>Tea</i>

19
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,510
Please enjoy.

20
00:01:42,550 --> 00:01:44,000
Bring some tea here.

21
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,230
Coming.

22
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:53,360
Excuse me.

23
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,270
Yes, Miss.

24
00:01:54,760 --> 00:01:57,160
Have you seen a young man
with Double Blades?

25
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,830
No.

26
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,120
Think again.

27
00:02:01,120 --> 00:02:03,040
He came from this direction

28
00:02:03,080 --> 00:02:04,870
and would’ve passed here.

29
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:06,590
I don’t remember seeing him.

30
00:02:06,590 --> 00:02:08,190
You can check with others.

31
00:02:11,270 --> 00:02:12,360
Hello, pretty.

32
00:02:12,360 --> 00:02:13,390
Are you

33
00:02:13,390 --> 00:02:16,000
looking for your husband?

34
00:02:18,830 --> 00:02:20,110
Relax.

35
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:21,960
What was he thinking

36
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:24,600
that he left you alone?

37
00:02:25,270 --> 00:02:26,550
Don’t worry.

38
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:28,830
I’ll look after you for him.

39
00:02:32,370 --> 00:02:33,080
Get lost!

40
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:39,630
Thank you, sir.

41
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:42,360
I’ve seen the one you’re looking for.

42
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:49,720
Wait, sir.

43
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,000
My lord,

44
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,630
these are the tongues of those

45
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:02,600
who insulted Miss Wu.

46
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,270
Feed them to the dogs.

47
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,190
Yes.

48
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,110
Where is she?

49
00:03:08,670 --> 00:03:10,320
I think she’s heading to the woods

50
00:03:10,320 --> 00:03:11,830
with that strange man.

51
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:15,270
Don’t worry.

52
00:03:15,270 --> 00:03:16,670
She’s still under our watch.

53
00:03:16,670 --> 00:03:17,520
Nothing will happen to her.

54
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,030
How can you be sure?

55
00:03:20,670 --> 00:03:21,910
Where are the woods?

56
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:23,110
I will go there myself.

57
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,080
Yes.

58
00:03:24,440 --> 00:03:25,160
And

59
00:03:25,830 --> 00:03:27,470
get me some plain clothes.

60
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:30,000
I don’t want her to recognize me.

61
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:30,880
Yes.

62
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:46,080
Sir,

63
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:48,030
where are we going?

64
00:03:51,630 --> 00:03:54,720
That man is about this tall

65
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,800
with Double Blades.

66
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,160
He seemed to be in a rush

67
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,360
as if he was looking for someone.

68
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,600
Yes. That’s him!

69
00:04:04,670 --> 00:04:06,470
<i>Forbidden Forest</i>
I saw him

70
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,000
going into this forest.

71
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,240
Thank you for telling me.

72
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:11,960
I’m going in and look for him.

73
00:04:11,960 --> 00:04:12,830
Hold on.

74
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:15,600
This place is dangerous.

75
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:19,440
Locals call it man-eating forest

76
00:04:19,440 --> 00:04:21,920
in which demons disguise as aged plants

77
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:23,200
to mislead humans

78
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,720
and devour their souls.

79
00:04:25,110 --> 00:04:26,880
Few can come out alive

80
00:04:26,880 --> 00:04:28,670
once they enter there.

81
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:31,200
Really?

82
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:33,510
<i>Forbidden Forest</i>

83
00:04:33,510 --> 00:04:36,600
The terrain seems unusual

84
00:04:36,600 --> 00:04:38,350
but follows the Eight-trigram.

85
00:04:38,350 --> 00:04:40,200
I heard some sects would use

86
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:42,270
such formations for safety

87
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:44,040
to keep outsiders away.

88
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,720
This forest must be one example.

89
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,880
I’m surprised

90
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:49,920
that you’re aware of that.

91
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,230
Do you know the way out?

92
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,480
I don’t.

93
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,000
I’ve only seen it once.

94
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:58,390
You don’t know?

95
00:04:58,950 --> 00:05:01,440
I thought that man had told you.

96
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,720
What a waste of time!

97
00:05:04,480 --> 00:05:05,200
Sir.

98
00:05:12,620 --> 00:05:15,740
<i>Forbidden Forest</i>

99
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,440
Hey, beauty.

100
00:05:31,790 --> 00:05:33,160
There’s no free meal.

101
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:35,320
Be honest with me.

102
00:05:35,350 --> 00:05:37,110
Do you have the Seal of Cautiousness?

103
00:05:38,830 --> 00:05:39,670
No.

104
00:05:39,670 --> 00:05:40,720
Liar!

105
00:05:41,350 --> 00:05:43,390
On the day of the Assembly,

106
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:45,070
the old bastard Chu Tianyu

107
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:47,830
stole that Seal from me,

108
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:50,200
but got killed by you.

109
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,880
If you don’t have it,

110
00:05:51,880 --> 00:05:53,440
where else could it be?

111
00:05:53,440 --> 00:05:54,950
That belongs to the Huos.

112
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,760
Why should I give it to you?

113
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:58,160
Listen,

114
00:05:58,160 --> 00:06:00,040
don’t push me!

115
00:06:01,950 --> 00:06:03,790
I thought

116
00:06:03,790 --> 00:06:06,110
Phoenix was decent

117
00:06:06,270 --> 00:06:07,550
and loyal.

118
00:06:08,070 --> 00:06:09,040
Turns out

119
00:06:09,040 --> 00:06:10,830
you’re no different

120
00:06:10,830 --> 00:06:12,160
from those rats

121
00:06:12,390 --> 00:06:14,510
who’d bite each other’s heads off

122
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:15,760
only for a bracelet.

123
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:20,110
Don’t degrade me to their level.

124
00:06:20,830 --> 00:06:22,510
I want the Seal back

125
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:24,790
simply because it’s the Huos’.

126
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:26,720
That has nothing to do

127
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,230
with the bracelet.

128
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:32,880
I don’t buy it.

129
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:35,000
Whatever.

130
00:06:36,790 --> 00:06:40,200
I heard it’s the key to divine skills.

131
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:44,040
Don’t you want them, Phoenix?

132
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:49,600
100 Destructive Palms are enough.

133
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:52,550
Why do I need other skills?

134
00:06:55,070 --> 00:06:57,790
As inexperienced as I am,

135
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,640
I’ve been told

136
00:07:01,390 --> 00:07:05,440
that you’re one of the most

137
00:07:05,670 --> 00:07:06,790
talented.

138
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:10,040
You were aggressive years back

139
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,830
and your Palms

140
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:16,390
are a double-edged sword.

141
00:07:17,640 --> 00:07:20,200
It’s invincible at the peak,

142
00:07:20,670 --> 00:07:22,480
but once you go downhill,

143
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:25,760
so will your skills.

144
00:07:25,760 --> 00:07:27,070
I had my doubts,

145
00:07:27,070 --> 00:07:28,600
but now,

146
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,040
that seems to be true.

147
00:07:33,790 --> 00:07:35,760
When I tested you,

148
00:07:35,760 --> 00:07:37,790
your moves were a bit slow,

149
00:07:38,510 --> 00:07:40,440
especially when I grabbed your jerkies.

150
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:42,510
Obviously,

151
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,720
your energy was low

152
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:49,110
which slowed down your Palms.

153
00:07:50,350 --> 00:07:51,160
Otherwise,

154
00:07:51,830 --> 00:07:54,510
how could I’ve dodged

155
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:56,640
the head of Four Guardians’ move?

156
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:01,320
Didn’t you see Zheng Luosheng

157
00:08:01,320 --> 00:08:03,390
as the head?

158
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,200
He’s nothing!

159
00:08:12,390 --> 00:08:14,070
Hey, beauty,

160
00:08:14,070 --> 00:08:16,040
are you flattering me

161
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,880
or scaring me?

162
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:27,110
I know how skilled I am.

163
00:08:27,550 --> 00:08:28,760
I’ve never placed any hope

164
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,510
on that bracelet.

165
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:33,230
I’m only after that Seal

166
00:08:33,230 --> 00:08:35,440
because no one else deserves it

167
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:38,960
other than the Huos.

168
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:46,200
The snow is about to stop.

169
00:08:47,110 --> 00:08:48,230
Phoenix,

170
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,670
once we’re out,

171
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:52,000
we’ll have to battle again.

172
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:01,470
I must say

173
00:09:01,470 --> 00:09:02,840
you have a big heart.

174
00:09:03,520 --> 00:09:05,080
Do you really believe

175
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,030
that I won’t kill you

176
00:09:07,030 --> 00:09:08,350
in your sleep?

177
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:11,200
Phoenix doesn’t kill beauties.

178
00:09:14,590 --> 00:09:15,520
You know me too well.

179
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:52,520
Fire Lotus is important to her.

180
00:09:52,520 --> 00:09:54,550
They won’t leave

181
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:57,230
and must be somewhere close.

182
00:10:17,710 --> 00:10:19,710
Wait.

183
00:10:19,710 --> 00:10:22,080
I’ve been here three times.

184
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,470
The formation here

185
00:10:25,470 --> 00:10:27,640
is more complicated
than that in the Huo’s.

186
00:10:28,030 --> 00:10:29,400
What to do?

187
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:31,470
How did Sheng get out last time?

188
00:10:38,710 --> 00:10:40,470
Miss, are you alright?

189
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:44,520
You’re...?

190
00:10:45,150 --> 00:10:45,640
A...

191
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,000
A woodcutter.

192
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,550
How did you get through

193
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,790
the Eight-trigram Formation?

194
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:53,200
I don’t know anything

195
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,760
other than cutting wood.

196
00:10:56,030 --> 00:10:58,760
Do you know the routes here?

197
00:11:01,030 --> 00:11:02,710
My friend is inside.

198
00:11:36,280 --> 00:11:38,320
Outsiders don’t know

199
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,080
there’s a cave deep in the woods.

200
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:42,520
A hothead with
Double Blades came earlier.

201
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:45,080
You must be looking for him, right?

202
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:45,880
Yes.

203
00:11:47,150 --> 00:11:48,320
The cave

204
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:49,760
belonged to a school

205
00:11:49,760 --> 00:11:51,960
that had been wiped out.

206
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:54,350
It’s right ahead.

207
00:11:54,350 --> 00:11:56,110
You can go there yourself.

208
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:02,030
Thanks.

209
00:12:07,030 --> 00:12:08,230
Sheng!

210
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:14,960
Sheng!

211
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:23,080
Chuchu,

212
00:12:23,710 --> 00:12:25,350
how did you get here?

213
00:12:26,230 --> 00:12:27,960
I asked around

214
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,670
and learned you left for this direction,

215
00:12:29,670 --> 00:12:30,960
so I followed you here.

216
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,760
I came to

217
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:35,520
check on Mr. Chongxiao.

218
00:12:35,520 --> 00:12:37,320
Hadn’t we agreed

219
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,520
to leave together

220
00:12:38,520 --> 00:12:40,520
and I’d share your burden?

221
00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:42,440
Yet you sneaked out alone.

222
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:44,280
I’m sorry.

223
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,400
It won’t happen again.

224
00:12:51,840 --> 00:12:53,230
Wu Chuchu,

225
00:12:54,150 --> 00:12:56,110
you’ll regret it.

226
00:13:06,710 --> 00:13:08,710
Are you with the Qi School?

227
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:10,230
How did you know

228
00:13:10,230 --> 00:13:12,280
the route?

229
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,960
I come in and out every day

230
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:16,520
to cut wood for a living.

231
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:18,230
I know this place like home.

232
00:13:18,230 --> 00:13:19,520
Have you seen someone

233
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,080
with Double Blades?

234
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,840
You know him?

235
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:27,790
More than that.

236
00:13:27,790 --> 00:13:29,030
He isn’t our member

237
00:13:29,030 --> 00:13:30,550
but he stole our skills.

238
00:13:30,550 --> 00:13:32,080
I must kill him!

239
00:13:35,910 --> 00:13:37,590
How come no one is here?

240
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:40,230
It’s where the Qi School used to be.

241
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,710
Did something happen

242
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:45,080
to Mr. Chongxiao?

243
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,960
Feng Wuyan!

244
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:57,000
Hand over that thing!

245
00:13:58,150 --> 00:13:59,150
What do you mean?

246
00:14:00,710 --> 00:14:02,280
Don’t play dumb.

247
00:14:03,550 --> 00:14:06,520
I saw you had that whisk at the inn.

248
00:14:11,230 --> 00:14:11,670
Let go of her!

249
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:13,320
Only if you give me that whisk!

250
00:14:16,280 --> 00:14:17,320
Don’t.

251
00:14:20,150 --> 00:14:21,470
Get it yourself.

252
00:14:22,320 --> 00:14:23,110
Let’s go!

253
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:26,110
A token of power.

254
00:14:27,550 --> 00:14:29,520
From now on,

255
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:32,400
I’m the chief of the Qi School.

256
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,840
I am the chief!

257
00:14:36,230 --> 00:14:38,030
Are you trying to kill me?

258
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:39,640
If not,

259
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:40,760
will you let me live?

260
00:14:40,760 --> 00:14:42,030
Listen,

261
00:14:42,030 --> 00:14:43,840
that old fart Chongxiao is dead.

262
00:14:46,110 --> 00:14:47,520
He was killed

263
00:14:47,520 --> 00:14:49,590
by the one who gave you the whisk.

264
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:54,760
A dead man’s wish isn’t important.

265
00:15:11,840 --> 00:15:13,080
You will need me

266
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,280
if you want to be the chief.

267
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:15,350
How so?

268
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:18,000
If Mr. Chongxiao is gone,

269
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,520
I’m the only one left

270
00:15:19,520 --> 00:15:21,960
with skills of the Qi School.

271
00:15:28,840 --> 00:15:30,200
Alright.

272
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:34,200
Tell me everything

273
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:35,640
that Chongxiao

274
00:15:35,640 --> 00:15:37,280
taught you

275
00:15:37,280 --> 00:15:38,640
if you want to live.

276
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,670
I can do it myself.

277
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:45,150
One move

278
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:48,030
and skills of the Qi School
will be gone forever.

279
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:52,200
When I

280
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:54,590
see your ancestors down there,

281
00:15:54,590 --> 00:15:56,790
what should I tell them?

282
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:06,740
<i>Great virtue is like water.</i>

283
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:26,030
It’s all your fault!

284
00:16:28,520 --> 00:16:29,500
You’re useless.

285
00:16:29,500 --> 00:16:30,790
<i>Great virtue is like water.</i>
Useless!

286
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:32,960
Useless!

287
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:36,030
What’s wrong? Stop beating yourself.

288
00:16:36,670 --> 00:16:37,960
When I was young,

289
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:41,030
I didn’t take those skills seriously.

290
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:44,710
But now, they’re almost lost.

