00:32:11,230 --> 00:32:13,950
and she looks fierce and pretty.

583
00:32:13,950 --> 00:32:16,070
Help! Help!

584
00:32:18,230 --> 00:32:18,880
Sir!

585
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:20,710
Mr. Li, what happened to Miss Wu?

586
00:32:20,710 --> 00:32:21,880
Can’t talk right now.

587
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:22,950
The Route Gang is well-connected.

588
00:32:22,950 --> 00:32:24,280
Could you ask around

589
00:32:24,280 --> 00:32:25,920
and tell me where Madam Nichang

590
00:32:25,920 --> 00:32:26,800
and the Yuyi Troupe are?

591
00:32:26,800 --> 00:32:27,950
After the Assembly,

592
00:32:27,950 --> 00:32:30,160
she decided to retire

593
00:32:30,160 --> 00:32:31,760
and returned to Qiaoyun House
in Hengyang.

594
00:32:31,760 --> 00:32:32,830
Hengyang?

595
00:32:32,830 --> 00:32:34,000
-Yes.
-Thanks.

596
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:35,520
Get me a carriage.

597
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:36,590
-We’re going there.
-Yes.

598
00:32:36,590 --> 00:32:38,590
Are you Miss Zhou Fei’s cousin?

599
00:32:38,590 --> 00:32:39,640
If you’re in a rush,

600
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:41,160
you can take our carriage.

601
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,710
Young Master Zhu.

602
00:32:42,710 --> 00:32:43,710
That’s great.

603
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,590
Thanks a ton.

604
00:32:44,590 --> 00:32:45,520
Don’t mention it, Mr. Li.

605
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:46,430
Let’s go.

606
00:32:46,430 --> 00:32:47,280
Without Miss Zhou,

607
00:32:47,280 --> 00:32:48,040
half of our members would’ve been killed

608
00:32:48,040 --> 00:32:49,800
by Ding Kui before the Assembly.

609
00:32:49,800 --> 00:32:51,350
Now, we’re at your disposal.

610
00:33:02,310 --> 00:33:06,430
Two, three, three, three,
four, left, right.

611
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,710
Left, right.

612
00:33:13,710 --> 00:33:16,230
What is this nonsense?

613
00:33:20,400 --> 00:33:22,400
Are you a member of the Qi School?

614
00:33:22,400 --> 00:33:24,560
If I knew the way out,

615
00:33:24,560 --> 00:33:26,280
I would’ve ditched you long ago.

616
00:33:27,350 --> 00:33:28,430
Alright.

617
00:33:29,280 --> 00:33:30,950
I’ll cut down all trees.

618
00:33:30,950 --> 00:33:33,000
Then we can get out.

619
00:33:34,710 --> 00:33:36,040
I dare you!

620
00:33:36,430 --> 00:33:38,040
Stay away from

621
00:33:38,040 --> 00:33:40,040
what belongs to our school.

622
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:42,070
Touch it

623
00:33:42,070 --> 00:33:43,710
and I’ll kill you.

624
00:33:52,310 --> 00:33:53,280
Commander,

625
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:55,470
Lord doesn’t receive any guests.

626
00:33:57,110 --> 00:34:00,070
I’m here to say goodbye.

627
00:34:04,680 --> 00:34:06,070
Let him in.

628
00:34:06,070 --> 00:34:06,880
Yes.

629
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,560
Tianying,

630
00:34:12,520 --> 00:34:14,080
