631
00:34:14,840 --> 00:34:17,520
Your flowers have grown even better.

632
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:20,190
Did you show up unannounced

633
00:34:20,190 --> 00:34:21,760
only to see my flowers?

634
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:25,000
I dare not

635
00:34:25,000 --> 00:34:26,600
go anywhere near them.

636
00:34:28,760 --> 00:34:31,040
Then why are you here?

637
00:34:31,910 --> 00:34:34,800
We maintain an army
to use it when necessary.

638
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:37,280
Ever since General Wu Fei’s incident
was exposed,

639
00:34:37,280 --> 00:34:39,190
tokens with ripple patterns
have appeared,

640
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:42,630
but the Demons have failed repeatedly.

641
00:34:42,630 --> 00:34:44,680
What’s the point

642
00:34:45,360 --> 00:34:46,650
of supporting them now?

643
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:53,870
Are you abandoning us?

644
00:34:54,230 --> 00:34:57,080
When Xiao Chuan clobbered you,

645
00:34:57,080 --> 00:34:58,430
you begged me

646
00:34:58,430 --> 00:35:00,670
to poison him with Bone-chilling.

647
00:35:01,630 --> 00:35:03,520
But that didn’t kill him.

648
00:35:04,520 --> 00:35:06,230
That was pure luck.

649
00:35:06,470 --> 00:35:07,500
I didn’t fail.

650
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,000
Yu Wenzhi,

651
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,080
