652
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:12,470
and betray the Demons,

653
00:35:12,470 --> 00:35:14,230
you know the consequence.

654
00:35:15,080 --> 00:35:16,600
A commander like you

655
00:35:16,840 --> 00:35:18,520
should be careful with

656
00:35:18,520 --> 00:35:20,230
what you say and do.

657
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,710
Tianying,

658
00:35:25,710 --> 00:35:27,470
you killed Li Zheng,

659
00:35:27,470 --> 00:35:29,390
poisoned Xiao Chuan
and robbed the Big Medicine Valley,

660
00:35:29,390 --> 00:35:31,560
leaving the world in awe.

661
00:35:31,560 --> 00:35:33,280
That’s why I chose to
work with the Demons

662
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,950
