687
00:36:41,950 --> 00:36:45,600
Only if you find them first.

688
00:36:54,470 --> 00:36:57,560
According to Tong Tianyang’s message,

689
00:36:58,390 --> 00:37:01,040
Chongxiao is one of the guardians

690
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:02,540
