697
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,090
Brother,

698
00:37:18,870 --> 00:37:21,470
I’ll find them for you

699
00:37:21,470 --> 00:37:23,560
at all costs.

700
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,470
My friend,

701
00:38:05,470 --> 00:38:06,800
