702
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,390
There’s more.

703
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:14,790
Miss.

704
00:38:16,760 --> 00:38:18,330
You must be Miss Zhou Fei, right?

705
00:38:19,560 --> 00:38:20,540
You know me?

706
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:22,520
Anzhi was

707
00:38:22,520 --> 00:38:23,840
