713
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:44,150
Miss!

714
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:49,360
Miss Zhou put her life on the line

715
00:38:49,360 --> 00:38:50,750
and went all the way

716
00:38:52,670 --> 00:38:54,680
to bring this Fire Lotus back

717
00:38:55,360 --> 00:38:58,710
to save you.

718
00:39:04,470 --> 00:39:05,510
That’s cold.

719
00:39:08,430 --> 00:39:09,640
But don’t worry.

720
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:12,140
Although she drained herself,

721
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:14,000
she’s back safe and sound.

722
00:39:16,150 --> 00:39:19,080
Heaven must be

723
00:39:19,080 --> 00:39:21,630
having mercy on you for your past

724
00:39:21,630 --> 00:39:24,000
so that you’re still alive

725
00:39:24,520 --> 00:39:28,040
and have met Miss Zhou Fei.

726
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:53,840
Madam!

727
00:39:54,360 --> 00:39:55,470
Take good care of yourself.

728
00:40:03,320 --> 00:40:05,360
It’s about time that you wake up.

729
00:40:06,630 --> 00:40:08,710
But too bad...

730
00:40:09,040 --> 00:40:09,980
Bad?

731
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:12,080
What’s bad?

732
00:40:12,080 --> 00:40:14,190
Everything is fine.

733
00:40:14,760 --> 00:40:16,910
Anzhi is feeling much better

734
00:40:16,910 --> 00:40:18,520
after taking the second herb.

735
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:20,430
When I said bad,

736
00:40:20,430 --> 00:40:22,430
I meant the timing.

737
00:40:23,840 --> 00:40:27,040
The herb brought him
out of his coma.

738
00:40:27,040 --> 00:40:28,430
He was waiting for you

739
00:40:28,430 --> 00:40:29,840
but had to

740
00:40:29,840 --> 00:40:32,390
go back to meditate yesterday.

741
00:40:36,670 --> 00:40:38,120
That’s good news.

742
00:40:38,800 --> 00:40:41,190
I’ll go get him the third herb,

743
00:40:41,190 --> 00:40:42,490
Flaming Sage.

744
00:40:49,670 --> 00:40:50,910
Hold your horses.

745
00:40:51,470 --> 00:40:53,840
It’s seldom seen

746
00:40:53,840 --> 00:40:55,120
and said

747
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:57,840
to only grow in the hot South Xinjiang.

748
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,280
That’s a thousand miles

749
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:03,560
from here.

750
00:41:03,560 --> 00:41:05,190
South Xinjiang?

751
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,910
Where the Small Medicine Valley is?

752
00:41:08,910 --> 00:41:10,190
Correct.

753
00:41:11,390 --> 00:41:14,360
As the head of that Valley,

754
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,280
Yang Jin must know something.

755
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:17,870
Even if he doesn’t,

756
00:41:18,390 --> 00:41:21,000
I can ask Ying Hecong about it.

757
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:22,520
Zhou Fei,

758
00:41:22,520 --> 00:41:24,000
